data.description: Check out this fully remodeled 3 bed 2 bath ranch tucked away in secluded neighborhood near Ravisloe Country Club. Step into the spacious open concept living room/dining room with luxury wood laminate flooring, 9.5-foot ceilings & tons of natural light. Kitchen features maple cabinets, stainless appliances & large island with plenty of counter space. Huge Master suite features wood burning fireplace, 2 closets, gorgeous bath with custom porcelain tiled walk-in shower & floors & NEW vanity & toilet. Additional 2 bedrooms feature 9.5-foot ceilings & very generous closet space. Full Bath features tiled tub/shower combo, LVP flooring & pleasant vanity. Huge linen closet offers tons of storage or option for main level laundry if desired. Mud room off back door offers great storage opportunity. Basement features finished laundry room with washer/dryer that stay. Unfinished portion of basement offers great storage. Huge oversized backyard almost fully fenced & patio paver area. 2 car garage. NEW solar panels with transferrable warranty offer great savings potential on utilities. NEW Furnace, A/C & 2 Electric Water Heaters. NEW Roof & Windows. Less than 1 mile to Metra. Short walk to downtown Homewood shopping & entertainment. Close to schools & Highway. This one has it all!
